To make your implementation to work, you should also declare/configure an authentication converter.

Something like this:

    @Component
    public class JwtAuthConverter implements Converter&lt;Jwt, AbstractAuthenticationToken&gt; {
    
      private JwtGrantedAuthoritiesConverter jwtGrantedAuthoritiesConverter;
    
      public JwtAuthConverter() {
        this.jwtGrantedAuthoritiesConverter = new JwtGrantedAuthoritiesConverter();
      }
    
      @Override
      public AbstractAuthenticationToken convert(Jwt jwt) {
        Collection&lt;GrantedAuthority&gt; authorities = Stream.concat(
            jwtGrantedAuthoritiesConverter.convert(jwt).stream(),
            extractAuthorities(jwt).stream()).collect(Collectors.toSet());
        return new JwtAuthenticationToken(jwt, authorities, getPrincipalClaimName(jwt));
      }
    
      private String getPrincipalClaimName(Jwt jwt) {
        return jwt.getClaim(JwtClaimNames.SUB);
      }
    
      private Collection&lt;GrantedAuthority&gt; extractAuthorities(Jwt jwt) {
        if (jwt.getClaim(&quot;authorities&quot;) != null) {
          Map&lt;String, Object&gt; realmAccess = jwt.getClaim(&quot;authorities&quot;);
          ObjectMapper mapper = new ObjectMapper();
          List&lt;String&gt; roles = mapper.convertValue(realmAccess.get(&quot;authority&quot;),
              new TypeReference&lt;List&lt;String&gt;&gt;() {
              });
          return roles.stream().map(role -&gt; new SimpleGrantedAuthority(&quot;SCOPE_&quot; + role))
              .collect(Collectors.toList());
        }
        return new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();
      }
    }

And also construct token with the `authorities` field something like this:

    &quot;authorities&quot;: {
        &quot;authority&quot;: [
            &quot;SCOPE_ESSENTIAL&quot;
              ...
          ]
         }

After all of this changes in  In `SecurityConfig {...}` class add next one field 

     private final JwtAuthConverter jwtAuthConverter;

Also in `filterChain` you should add this convertor:

replace: 

    .oauth2ResourceServer(oauth2 -&gt; oauth2.jwt(jwt -&gt; jwt.decoder(jwtDecoder())))

TO

    oauth2ResourceServer(oauth2 -&gt;
    
            oauth2.jwt(jwt -&gt; {
    
                jwt.decoder(jwtDecoder());
                jwt.jwtAuthenticationConverter(jwtAuthConverter);
            }));

